data.description: See your absolutely beautiful new Lake Blackshear home today!  Enjoy this Classic Southern Living Plan located on Cedar Creek - outstanding fishing and just  minutes away from water sports on the main!  Spacious living room with a stacked stone fireplace, vaulted ceiling  and built in cabinets  leads out to the deck and and the lake! New flooring on the main level. Spacious dining room.  Love the cook's kitchen and the oversized laundry room !  Makes organization a cinch !   The master bedroom  has recently been remodeled & you'll enjoy that soaking tub!   2 bedroom and 2 baths downstairs with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths upstairs! Oversized garage,  paved driveway and remodeled dock!  Deep fishing hole near the dock ! Outstanding fulltime , weekend or investment home!  Great neighborhood !  Fine home !  Gorgeous property!  Immaculate & move in ready!! Bring the boat!
